===Etymology 4===
{{zh-forms|alt=戍,茨,㢀,𡪣,次,聚,陬,宿,處,室-Hainan}}
Traditionally thought to be derived from etymology 3 ({{zh-ref|Huang (1988)}}), but its etymology is disputed. {{zh-ref|Norman (1984)}} argues for a derivation from {{och-l|戍|to garrison the frontier}}, while {{zh-ref|Zhengzhang (2014)}} proposes that it is from {{och-l|處|id=2|residence}}. {{zh-ref|Zeng et al. (2024)}} argue that it descended from {{och-l|舍|id=2|lodging-house}}.

